        <Replace Tag="LOC_HONKAI_TECH_PERCEPTION_NAME" Language="zh_Hans_CN"><Text>崩坏能感知</Text></Replace>
        <Replace Tag="LOC_HONKAI_TECH_PERCEPTION_DESC" Language="zh_Hans_CN"><Text>消耗 {1_Amount} [ICON_HONKAI_RESEARCH] 崩坏能研究点[NEWLINE][NEWLINE]一切的开始。解锁战术崩坏能产出。</Text></Replace>
        <Replace Tag="LOC_HONKAI_TECH_OMEN_NAME" Language="zh_Hans_CN"><Text>崩坏预兆</Text></Replace>
        <Replace Tag="LOC_HONKAI_TECH_OMEN_DESC" Language="zh_Hans_CN"><Text>消耗 {1_Amount} [ICON_HONKAI_RESEARCH] 崩坏能研究点[NEWLINE][NEWLINE]每回合无条件 +1 信仰值。（极速抢发万神殿）</Text></Replace>
        <Replace Tag="LOC_HONKAI_TECH_PATHOLOGY_NAME" Language="zh_Hans_CN"><Text>崩坏病理学</Text></Replace>
        <Replace Tag="LOC_HONKAI_TECH_PATHOLOGY_DESC" Language="zh_Hans_CN"><Text>消耗 {1_Amount} [ICON_HONKAI_RESEARCH] 崩坏能研究点[NEWLINE][NEWLINE]城市免疫部分崩坏灾难导致的宜居度惩罚。</Text></Replace>
        <Replace Tag="LOC_HONKAI_TECH_BASIC_TACTICS_NAME" Language="zh_Hans_CN"><Text>基础抗崩坏战术</Text></Replace>
        <Replace Tag="LOC_HONKAI_TECH_BASIC_TACTICS_DESC" Language="zh_Hans_CN"><Text>消耗 {1_Amount} [ICON_HONKAI_RESEARCH] 崩坏能研究点[NEWLINE][NEWLINE]解锁军事政策卡【崩坏抗击操典】。</Text></Replace>
        <Replace Tag="LOC_HONKAI_TECH_ENERGY_CONTAINER_NAME" Language="zh_Hans_CN"><Text>能源容器雏形</Text></Replace>
        <Replace Tag="LOC_HONKAI_TECH_ENERGY_CONTAINER_DESC" Language="zh_Hans_CN"><Text>消耗 {1_Amount} [ICON_HONKAI_RESEARCH] 崩坏能研究点[NEWLINE][NEWLINE]解锁初级【崩坏能存储池】建筑。</Text></Replace>
        <Replace Tag="LOC_HONKAI_TECH_DESTINY_CLERGY_NAME" Language="zh_Hans_CN"><Text>命运神职</Text></Replace>
        <Replace Tag="LOC_HONKAI_TECH_DESTINY_CLERGY_DESC" Language="zh_Hans_CN"><Text>消耗 {1_Amount} [ICON_HONKAI_RESEARCH] 崩坏能研究点[NEWLINE][NEWLINE]解锁【天命总部】、【天命大教堂】与天命支部 T1 建筑【天命礼拜堂】，并提升天命支部建设速度。</Text></Replace>
        <Replace Tag="LOC_HONKAI_TECH_NUN_FORMATION_NAME" Language="zh_Hans_CN"><Text>天命修女编制</Text></Replace>
        <Replace Tag="LOC_HONKAI_TECH_NUN_FORMATION_DESC" Language="zh_Hans_CN"><Text>消耗 {1_Amount} [ICON_HONKAI_RESEARCH] 崩坏能研究点[NEWLINE][NEWLINE]允许使用信仰值购买女武神单位，并降低其购买费用。</Text></Replace>
