        <Replace Tag="LOC_HONKAI_TECH_SCHICKSAL_DOCTRINE_DESC" Language="zh_Hans_CN"><Text>消耗 {1_Amount} [ICON_HONKAI_RESEARCH] 崩坏能研究点[NEWLINE][NEWLINE]解锁军事政策卡【天命教义】与天命支部 T2 建筑【赎罪庭】。</Text></Replace>
        <Replace Tag="LOC_HONKAI_TECH_PRAYER_ROOM_NAME" Language="zh_Hans_CN"><Text>祈祷室基建</Text></Replace>
        <Replace Tag="LOC_HONKAI_TECH_PRAYER_ROOM_DESC" Language="zh_Hans_CN"><Text>消耗 {1_Amount} [ICON_HONKAI_RESEARCH] 崩坏能研究点[NEWLINE][NEWLINE]解锁特色改良【祈祷室】。女武神自带 3 次建造次数，可直接修建该改良。</Text></Replace>
        <Replace Tag="LOC_HONKAI_TECH_HONKAI_CONDUCTION_NAME" Language="zh_Hans_CN"><Text>崩坏能传导</Text></Replace>
        <Replace Tag="LOC_HONKAI_TECH_HONKAI_CONDUCTION_DESC" Language="zh_Hans_CN"><Text>消耗 {1_Amount} [ICON_HONKAI_RESEARCH] 崩坏能研究点[NEWLINE][NEWLINE]国内商路为出发城市提供额外战术崩坏能，数值取决于该城的特色区域基础值。</Text></Replace>
        <Replace Tag="LOC_HONKAI_TECH_ATONEMENT_SYSTEM_NAME" Language="zh_Hans_CN"><Text>赎罪体系</Text></Replace>
        <Replace Tag="LOC_HONKAI_TECH_ATONEMENT_SYSTEM_DESC" Language="zh_Hans_CN"><Text>消耗 {1_Amount} [ICON_HONKAI_RESEARCH] 崩坏能研究点[NEWLINE][NEWLINE]击杀敌方单位时，获得等同于被击败单位战斗力 100% 的信仰值。</Text></Replace>
        <Replace Tag="LOC_HONKAI_TECH_KNIGHT_LEGACY_NAME" Language="zh_Hans_CN"><Text>骑士传承</Text></Replace>
        <Replace Tag="LOC_HONKAI_TECH_KNIGHT_LEGACY_DESC" Language="zh_Hans_CN"><Text>消耗 {1_Amount} [ICON_HONKAI_RESEARCH] 崩坏能研究点[NEWLINE][NEWLINE]解锁军事政策卡【天命骑士誓约】，女武神按当前所在己方城市的城墙等级获得战斗力。</Text></Replace>
        <Replace Tag="LOC_HONKAI_TECH_POWER_ARMOR_NAME" Language="zh_Hans_CN"><Text>圣血构装预想</Text></Replace>
        <Replace Tag="LOC_HONKAI_TECH_POWER_ARMOR_DESC" Language="zh_Hans_CN"><Text>消耗 {1_Amount} [ICON_HONKAI_RESEARCH] 崩坏能研究点[NEWLINE][NEWLINE]解锁军事政策卡【圣血构装】，所有女武神战斗力 +4。</Text></Replace>
        <Replace Tag="LOC_HONKAI_TECH_VALKYRIE_ADVANCED_NAME" Language="zh_Hans_CN"><Text>女武神进阶教材</Text></Replace>
        <Replace Tag="LOC_HONKAI_TECH_VALKYRIE_ADVANCED_DESC" Language="zh_Hans_CN"><Text>消耗 {1_Amount} [ICON_HONKAI_RESEARCH] 崩坏能研究点[NEWLINE][NEWLINE]帝国女武神训练等级 +1，优化动态评级概率。</Text></Replace>
        <Replace Tag="LOC_HONKAI_TECH_KEY_OF_FINALITY_NAME" Language="zh_Hans_CN"><Text>终焉之钥</Text></Replace>
        <Replace Tag="LOC_HONKAI_TECH_KEY_OF_FINALITY_DESC" Language="zh_Hans_CN"><Text>消耗 {1_Amount} [ICON_HONKAI_RESEARCH] 崩坏能研究点[NEWLINE][NEWLINE]最终权限。</Text></Replace>

